FOUR STRONG/HACKNEY, J.V., by and through its liquidating partner, Four Strong Builders, Inc., Plaintiff-Appellant, v. UNITED STATES, Defendant-Appellee. No. 02-5138. United States Court of Appeals, Federal Circuit. DECIDED: Feb. 12, 2003.

*924Before NEWMAN, Circuit Judge, PLAGER, Senior Circuit Judge, and BRYSON, Circuit Judge.

JUDGMENT

PER CURIAM.

This CAUSE having been heard and considered, it is ORDERED and ADJUDGED: AFFIRMED. See Fed. Cir. R. 36
